        "created_at": "2020-06-29T22:03:13.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I would say this is right in the first sweet spot.  It certainly isn\u2019t a fully mature Champagne with tertiary flavors etc.  But it\u2019s solidly in that first window where the initial, primary flavors have integrated.  It\u2019s fresh and sturdy but open.</p>",
